cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DL

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on cross-lingual transfer learning using neural encoder-decoder models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DL (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves transfer learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper uses neural networks to improve performance, which is a common technique in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
